snippet: An Israeli woman was stabbed to death in Etzion block as violence flared with three Palestinians carrying out separate attacks in the occupied West Bank.
abstract: Israelis civilians and soldiers shoot and kill three Palestinians who had attacked Israeli Jews in separate incidents throughout day; one Israeli woman is killed in attacks.

byline.contributor: Rami Nazzal contributed reporting from Ramallah, West Bank, and Myra Noveck from Jerusalem.

lead_paragraph: An Israeli woman was stabbed to death in Etzion block as violence flared with three Palestinians carrying out separate attacks in the occupied West Bank.

headline.main: Israeli Woman and 3 Palestinian Attackers Killed in West Bank
headline.print_headline: West Bank Faces Spate of Assaults That Kill 4
